{% from "components/avatar-image/macro.njk" import avatarImage %}

<p>An <code>AvatarImage</code> renders an <code>&lt;img&gt;</code>
  with <code>loading="lazy"</code> and an empty default
  <code>alt</code> so it composes cleanly inside an
  <a href="/components/avatar/"><code>Avatar</code></a> (the
  surrounding avatar carries the accessible name).</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/avatar/">Avatar demo</a> for a
  composed example. When used standalone outside an Avatar, pass
  a meaningful <code>alt</code> via params.</p>
